  "elapsed_s": 14.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he, and he spoke a great deal about Israel-- that is Palestine at that time-- especially.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he was very supportive of these-- of illegal immigration, the Halutzim projects.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Whether you were aware of at that time, young people would train in countries in Europe, getting ready for Palestine-- to emigrate illegally to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they would train on farms.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They would set-- set up a collective farm for the Halutzim pioneers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We are talking about boys and girls in their late teens or mid teens.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They would spend a year or two on the collectives, get ready-- get acquainted with farming [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] mainly.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And eventually, they would emigrate.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "These were the pioneers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "These were the people-- the sort of people who, when they arrived to Palestine in their, early 30s, late 20s, these were the people who really, who dried the swamps, who did all the dirty work, who eventually became the leaders of-- when Palestine became a state, when, when Palestine became Israel.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
